  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Kdebase-Runtime</title>

    <para>kdebase-runtime is for runtime dependencies and is a required 
    package for <application>KDE</application> applications like kdesu, 
    kfile etc.</para>

    &lfs67_checked;

